    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {className: a3; text-align: left;}\n.html-preview .a5 {className: a5; text-align: left;}\n.html-preview .a7 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a7\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #auto;\">Ишончли вакил иштирокида тузилган кўчмас мол-мулк олди-сотди шартномасининг тасдиқлов ёзуви</span></p>\n<p class=\"a7\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Тасдиқлов ёзуви ёзилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> куни ушбу шартномани мен - Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Нотариал идора жойлашган ҳудуд </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да жойлашган хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи нотариус </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> тарафларнинг хоҳиш-иродасига ва Ўзбекистон Республикаси қонун ҳужжатларига асосан тасдиқладим.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Шартнома тарафлар томонидан менинг ҳузуримда ўқиб, имзолади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Тарафларнинг шахси аниқланди, уларнинг муомалага лаёқатлилиги ва сотилаётган уй-жой сотувчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Уй-жойни сотган шахснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га тегишлилиги ва ишончли вакил - </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Уй-жой сотилишида қатнашган сотувчи вакилининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг ваколати текширилди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Шахсий мулоқот давомида тарафларнинг муомалага лаёқатсизлигига шубҳа туғилмади ва ушбу нотариал ҳаракатни амалга ошириш даврида нотариал идорада уларнинг муомалага лаёқатсизликлари ҳақида ҳеч қандай маълумотлар йўқ.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 481-моддасига асосан ушбу шартнома </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Шартнома рўйхатдан ўтказилиши лозим бўлган туман (шаҳар) кадастр бўлими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> Иқтисодиёт ва молия вазирлиги ҳузуридаги Кадастр агентлигида давлат рўйхатидан ўтказилиши лозим.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Реестрга </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Шартноманинг реестр рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-сон билан қайд қилинди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Давлат божи: </span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#4}Ундириладиган давлат божи миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ҳуқуқий ва техник тусдаги қўшимча ҳаракатлар учун ундириладиган тўловлар: </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ҳуқуқий ва техник тусдаги қўшимча ҳаракатлар учун ундириладиган тўловлар миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Нотариус: </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>(имзо)</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">М.Ў.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p> </p>\n</div></div>",
